---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="訊息已送出" noindex>
  <section class="blueprint-grid grid min-h-[65svh] place-items-center py-20 text-center">
    <div class="container-shell">
      <p class="eyebrow justify-center">Message Received</p>
      <h1 class="section-title mt-6">收到，多謝你。</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-steel-300">我們會盡快查看你的訊息。你亦可以先回到知識庫繼續閱讀。</p>
      <a href="/blog/" class="button-primary mt-8">返回文章 →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
